OL,3,CMajor Birmingham hospital's maternity
OL,4,Cservices must 'rapidly improve', CQC
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe maternity services at City
OL,8,FHospital have been rated as "requires
OL,9,Fimprovement" after an inspection by
OL,10,Fthe Care Quality Commission (CQC).
OL,12,FIt was investigated in June after
OL,13,Fconcerns had been raised by whistle-
OL,14,Fblowers about poor culture, staff
OL,15,Fshortages, long waits to be induced
OL,16,Fand a lack of thorough investigation
OL,17,Fof serious incidents.
