OL,3,CMajor Birmingham hospital's maternity
OL,4,Cservices must 'rapidly improve', CQC
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe maternity service was rated
OL,8,F"inadequate" for safety, and its
OL,9,Frating for both quality leadership and
OL,10,Fsafety has dropped from "good" to
OL,11,F"requires improvement".
OL,13,FThe hospital, part of Sandwell and
OL,14,FWest Birmingham Hospitals NHS Trust,
OL,15,Foverall, has previously been rated as
OL,16,F"requires improvement."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
