OL,3,CMajor Birmingham hospital's maternity
OL,4,Cservices must 'rapidly improve', CQC
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe CQC said the Trust should focus
OL,8,Fits attention on making "significant
OL,9,Fimprovements around the environment,
OL,10,Fequipment, safeguarding, use of
OL,11,Finterpreters and staffing."
OL,13,FCharlotte Rudge, CQC deputy director
OL,14,Fof operations in the Midlands, said:
OL,15,F"We found leaders needed to rapidly
OL,16,Fimprove a number of areas to make care
OL,17,Fsafer for women, people using the
OL,18,Fservice and their babies."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
