OL,3,CMajor Birmingham hospital's maternity
OL,4,Cservices must 'rapidly improve', CQC
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FShe highlighted staffing as "a
OL,8,Fsignificant problem", before adding
OL,9,Fthat staff were not always
OL,10,Fappropriately trained.
OL,12,FStaff reported they didn't always have
OL,13,Ftime to carry out safeguarding
OL,14,Fprocedures.
OL,16,FOne positive area they highlighted was
OL,17,Fthe hospital staff's work to support
OL,18,Fequality, diversity and inclusion.
