OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMs Rudge said they found: "staff used
OL,8,Fflashcards to communicate with people
OL,9,Fwho were deaf or had a learning
OL,10,Fdisability, and they were also trying
OL,11,Fto produce handy guides when caring
OL,12,Ffor people living with anxiety,
OL,13,Fdeafness, blindness, and those who
OL,14,Fidentified as trans or non-binary to
OL,15,Fhelp with communication concerns."
OL,17,FShe added: "Since the inspection,
OL,18,Fthey've produced an action plan to
OL,19,Faddress our concerns and have
OL,20,Fcompleted all actions.
